column2: select w.*, round(p.ra,#) as ra, round(p.dec,#) as dec, round(p.mjd, #) as mjd, p.plate as plate, p.fiberID as fiber,   p.z, p.zErr, p.zWarning, p.class, p.subClass, p.z_noqso, p.zErr_noqso, p.zWarning_noqso, p.snMedian, p.sourceType,   p.specObjID, p.bestObjID, p.spectroFlux_u,p.spectroFlux_g,p.spectroFlux_r,p.spectroFlux_i,p.spectroFlux_z  into mydb.TDSS_PREV_SpecObjAllDR1# from mydb.TDSS_candidates_all_PREV w cross apply dbo.fGetNearbyObjAllEq(w.ra,w.dec, #) N, SpecObjAll p where p.bestObjID = N.objID and p.targetType=&&&
